summary: An ordinance relating to zoning, and providing for the rezoning of an unplatted tract of land, approximately 190 feet in width, extending from McClellan Street to Bayview Street, the east line of said tract being approximately the east line of 28th Avenue South, produced south, with repsect to Use, Height and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections, numbered 2-22, 10-1, and 17-18, respectively.
